{"tid":1592943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[FC]大家可唔可以用下腦上連登","createTime":"2019-09-25T00:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T14:02:53.000Z","uid":20820,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4d5d6e17553d5a59daf6cdb2f6d3f68d5918ffec","tid":1592943,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T00:13:48.000Z","msg":"唔知大家覺唔覺連登已經變返3個月前既兒登<br />\n如果想繼續落去可唔可以帶腦上網<br />\n唔好俾垃圾comment spin走討論方向<br />\n唔好比黑警講廢話浪費時間<br />\n所有野用common sense諗下真偽<br />\n同埋之前有人提過，唔好花時間落傳聞<br />\n<br />\nand自己小小意見，獅鳥只係合理自衛，唔係抗爭之一，只不過我地以前冇做過咁解"},{"pid":"c0074b29b677a9d8977b08a295c6b6086e0528c7","tid":1592943,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T00:14:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"8a6526d51fadf233c551cfc79fe47d53782df30f","tid":1592943,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T00:16:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7febc53e4133d752db1d48e03c62bc9a7395ca46","tid":1592943,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T00:21:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oW1Kuu1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoW1Kuu1.jpg&h=62d8c14b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56197c16619290e3b7bdfc7aaf223653c5522f83","tid":1592943,"uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T00:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2a9f606b7dee750e281afe4ac05692ee91de23","tid":1592943,"uid":15921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T00:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/